data.description: Fantastic Herriman Home showcases gorgeous Mountain Views and is ideally situated at the end of the road providing a private lifestyle! Formal, front Living Room can easily be used as a Home Office, Library, Music Room and more. Discover the Open Great Room with abundant 2-story windows allowing for abundant natural lighting, soaring ceilings and second floor balcony overlooks the inviting Great Room! Gorgeous Kitchen includes contrast flooring, rich cabinetry with crown molding, Quartz tops, expansive island, subway tile backsplash, SS appliances including a gas stove and pendant lighting! Fauxwood flooring flows to connected Dining Area with Mudroom/Garage access and Backyard ease-of-access via sliding glass doors. Upstairs Master Bedroom Suite includes tray ceiling, walk-in closet with custom shelving and Master Suite Bathroom showcasing rich cabinetry, expansive double sink vanity, separate corner soaking tub and standing glass shower! Room to grow in the expansive basement Family Room offering endless possibilities await to entertain. Spacious .14 acre lot boasts sought after mountain views and large, unoccupied wilderness space behind the home! Ideally located near Blackridge Reservoir, Secret Canyon Trailhead, Thorley & Driffield Park, various Hiking and Biking trails, Mountain View Corridor, Mountain View Village shopping, dining, entertainment and more! A short drive to Bangerter Highway, I-15, Silicon Slopes, Thanksgiving Point, just to name a few. Come tour this fantastic home today!
